flying in the last 90 days.

00:04:07.060 --> 00:04:08.980
Anyway, so they
just try to fit--

00:04:08.980 --> 00:04:12.280
they try to say, how challenging
is this flight, how experienced

00:04:12.280 --> 00:04:15.580
are you in general, how
experienced are you recently,

00:04:15.580 --> 00:04:17.360
