00:07:10.500 --> 00:07:13.650
So think about it.

00:07:13.650 --> 00:07:15.270
Roll is really the
lateral motion.

00:07:15.270 --> 00:07:17.840
But it's around the
longitudinal axis.

00:07:17.840 --> 00:07:21.000
So don't get confused there.

00:07:21.000 --> 00:07:26.045
Remember why Johnny Cessna can't
hover is also a limit for--

00:07:26.045 --> 00:07:27.420
this limits
everything basically.

00:07:27.420 --> 00:07:30.780
The stalling angle of attack
is why you need a helicopter

00:07:30.780 --> 00:07:32.400
if you want to hover.

00:07:32.400 --> 00:07:36.690
And it is why you need to
maintain a reasonable airspeed

00:07:36.690 --> 00:07:37.890
