00:08:02.640 --> 00:08:04.590
It's the angle of
attack and your ability

00:08:04.590 --> 00:08:07.140
to deflect air molecules down.

00:08:07.140 --> 00:08:08.730
That's what generates lift.

00:08:08.730 --> 00:08:12.330
