00:11:12.450 --> 00:11:17.700
Unstable air leads
to cumulus clouds.

00:11:17.700 --> 00:11:20.250
They can become
cumulonimbus clouds.

00:11:20.250 --> 00:11:23.280
And now you have a
really bad hazard

00:11:23.280 --> 00:11:26.910
to aviation with terrible icing,
terrible turbulence, maybe

00:11:26.910 --> 00:11:29.550
hail.

