00:15:17.790 --> 00:15:20.260
for charger and scheduled
airline service,

00:15:20.260 --> 00:15:22.360
they show you that there
are some extra safety

00:15:22.360 --> 00:15:25.460
margins that can be built in.

00:15:25.460 --> 00:15:29.695
Night flying advice
you just heard.

00:15:29.695 --> 00:15:31.320
Remember, as the
