00:15:31.320 --> 00:15:36.990
responsible for keeping
the airplane airworthy

00:15:36.990 --> 00:15:39.450
if you do choose to go
out and buy an aircraft.

00:15:39.450 --> 00:15:42.160
So these responsibilities
are for most of you going

00:15:42.160 --> 00:15:44.190
to be on the flight school.

00:15:44.190 --> 00:15:48.630
However, you're still the
final authority as the pilot.

00:15:48.630 --> 00:15:52.730
And you can deviate from
the rules in an emergency.

00:15:52.730 --> 00:15:55.260
And you only have to report
the deviation if requested.

00:15:55.260 --> 00:15:57.780
I think the feds like to
ask this on the knowledge

00:15:57.780 --> 00:16:00.395
test, because the natural
answer is, of course,

00:16:00.395 --> 00:16:01.770
