00:16:01.770 --> 00:16:04.050
And I declared it an emergency,
and I broke the rules.

00:16:04.050 --> 00:16:05.670
But you don't actually
have to report

00:16:05.670 --> 00:16:07.200
that unless they ask you to.

00:16:07.200 --> 00:16:09.540
TINA SRIVASTAVA: But even
